<p>Return the patients consent records that exist with the supplied NHS number and have a category of "NOOM" to indicate these are National Opt-Out records that exclude Type 2 objections.</p> 

<div markdown="span" class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
GET {{include.base}}{{include.resource}}?patient=[NHS Number]&category=[Category Type]</div>

<div class="language-http highlighter-rouge">
<pre class="highlight"><code><span class="err">GET {{include.base}}{{include.resource}}?patient=4021341212&category=NOOM
</span></code>
Return {{include.resource}} resource that has a patient value of {{include.text1}} and a category of {{include.text2}}.</pre>
</div>

<p>Return patient consent record with the supplied NHS number and have a purpose code of HRESCH to retrieve a National Opt-Out research only objection record.</p> 

<div markdown="span" class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
