<div class="language-http highlighter-rouge">
<pre class="highlight"><code><span class="err">GET {{include.base}}{{include.resource}}?patient=https://nww.spine.nhs.uk/4505577104&purpose=HRESCH
</span></code>
Return {{include.resource}} resource that has a patient value of {{include.text1}} and a purpose of {{include.text3}}.</pre>
</div>

